## Generating New Test Files
When asked to generate a test file:
1. Reference the corresponding section number in `tests/specs/ohm-test-suite.md`
2. Create or reuse the Page Object for that area
3. Follow naming: `[feature-area].spec.ts`
4. Include all test cases from the spec section — stub as `test.skip()` if not yet implementable
5. Add comment at top with spec section number and source

